import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { FormStore } from "./FormStore"
import { Playground, PropsTable } from "docz"

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"form-store"}}>{`Form Store`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"store"}}>{`Store`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"we-are-using-json-forms"}}>{`We are using JSON Forms.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`FormStore allows easy access to create new forms based on these schemas.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Below you will find some useful links on how JSON Schema Forms work.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://mozilla-services.github.io/react-jsonschema-form/"}}>{`JSON Forms Playground`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://github.com/mozilla-services/react-jsonschema-form"}}>{`JSON Forms Documentation`}</MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
